## Contact Link Field

A field that captures a contact link (email, phone, or URL) and renders an appropriate icon plus a click-through action.

### Usage

```ts
import { CardDef, field, contains } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import ContactLinkField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/contact-link';

export class Example extends CardDef {
  @field contact = contains(ContactLinkField);
}
```
